    <section id="id14741971">
      <title>Assessment</title>
      <para id="id16923614"><emphasis effect="bold">Learning Outcome 1:</emphasis> The learner will be able to recognise, describe and represent numbers and their relationships, and to count, estimate, calculate and check with competence and confidence in solving problems.</para>
      <para id="id11099784"><emphasis effect="bold">Assessment Standard 1.3:</emphasis> We know this when the learner recognises and represents the following numbers in order to describe and compare them:</para>
      <para id="id16723839"><emphasis effect="bold">1.3.6:</emphasis> multiples and factors of at least any 2-digit and 3-digit whole number.</para>
    </section>
